- And what about you?
- Go find help.

47:52.522 --> 47:54.222
There's a fire brigade two blocks down.

47:54.257 --> 47:55.857
They've probably already seen the smoke.

47:55.858 --> 47:57.759
I'll go up the stairs
and wait it out up there.

47:57.760 --> 47:59.193
- Now, go. You've got to go.
- I won't.

47:59.195 --> 48:00.729
Neely, you're running out of time!

48:00.730 --> 48:03.799
Go! Get on this ladder and go now.

48:05.768 --> 48:09.204
That's it. Climb down as far as you can.

48:09.205 --> 48:12.374
Oh, God.

48:12.375 --> 48:14.743
That's it, Neely. Go.

48:14.744 --> 48:16.812
As far as you can go.

48:19.048 --> 48:20.749
That's it.

48:22.752 --> 48:24.453
Good, now let go.

48:24.454 --> 48:26.755
Now, Neely. Now!

48:32.927 --> 48:35.729
Neely? Neely?

48:35.730 --> 48:37.998
Neely, are you all right?

48:39.034 --> 48:40.901
Go get help.

48:40.902 --> 48:43.471
Go.

48:43.472 --> 48:45.339
Now.

49:15.468 --> 49:17.703
Where?

49:20.808 --> 49:22.608
Dad!

49:30.450 --> 49:32.484
No! No!

49:41.527 --> 49:43.794
Shh, shh.

50:11.056 --> 50:13.357
Oh, God.

50:22.099 --> 50:24.701
Oh, God.

50:30.241 --> 50:31.875
We're almost there.

50:31.909 --> 50:34.678
We should talk about compensation.

50:34.712 --> 50:38.047
No, I'm not much interested in money.

50:40.518 --> 50:44.687
You know, I fund a hospital in New York.

50:44.688 --> 50:46.889
The Knickerbocker.

50:46.923 --> 50:50.425
Isn't that where J.M. Christiansen is?

50:50.460 --> 50:53.361
I hear he's doing some astonishing work.

50:55.565 --> 50:57.566
You two should meet.

50:57.567 --> 50:58.934
I'll introduce you.

